</p><p class="- topic/p ">On the service laptop, the TSM application makes also use of the SAM key. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">A service engineer has typical 1 SAM key and in practice within the system it is handy to use the TSM on the laptop and use the SDS and ADAM at the same time. 
